{"tid":1782964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《公投第二擊》去中國化網購平台-加唔加設美元付款結算？","createTime":"2019-12-14T11:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T16:51:46.000Z","uid":287062,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a334b422a0d6b5c4fe048de1a10dccac544bf909","tid":1782964,"uid":287062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:43:12.000Z","msg":"公投第一擊回帶：<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1781528/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1781528/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n經過公投後，我哋會順應民意<span style=\"color: red;\">唔用順豐送貨</span>！第二個公投嘅問題係：去中國化網購平台加唔加設美元付款結算好呢？<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n- 令香港網購零售開始用美元結算，培養大眾習慣使用美元<br />\n- 只要有一個成功，就可以令更多小商店彷效<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n- 收美元會增加營運成本，有匯率差價，產品定價有機會未能太貼近市價<br />\n- 由於會蝕匯率，入貨時候要用港幣，短期盈利減少<br />\n<br />\n重溫一下我哋嘅去中國化網購平台：<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1779516/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1779516/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公投：<br />\n正評-兩樣都接受，有得揀會試下用美金<br />\n負評-唔好煩，用返港幣就夠<br />\n<br />\n另外希望大家可以分享下會使用美金嘅比率，等我地做個參考！<br />\n<br />\n有咩意見想我哋留意返，都歡迎留言提出<br />\nContact us: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/cgh852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcgh852&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=cf0f0ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cgh852</a> <br />\n<br />\nTG Channel: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/notfromchina\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnotfromchina&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=d35d6ce9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/notfromchina</a>"},{"pid":"e27886ea4c5aac78ef184d91624ed52b19c17ef4","tid":1782964,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"945194d07a28fc159b375255e788b1343cdd00e9","tid":1782964,"uid":55229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"用美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa58d119c1aa1e6b126d5ffc5959c0a0a0a324af","tid":1782964,"uid":287062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">網上購物平台、支付服務、運輸全部收歸國有，整個網購產業鏈收購完成。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黨係有幾重視網購，先會國有化整個產業鏈? <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">凡是敵人擁護的，我哋就要抗衡！所以我哋即將推出一個抵制中國貨嘅網購平台，所得盈利用嚟聘請手足，發展小額資助計劃。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n平台各部門大致上都已埋班，但以下依然要人!!!<br />\n文宣<br />\nMarketing<br />\n黃業主倉介紹<br />\n有非中國製既供應商"},{"pid":"153cf93fdda16b164bc22e8a25b87d073f2d0aff","tid":1782964,"uid":287062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"平台理念：<br />\n1 完全<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔會有MADE IN CHINA產品</span></span><br />\n-尋找本港或外國廠商同優質產品<br />\n-可以好安心盡情係度買野，唔怕買到大劣貨<br />\n<br />\n2 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">橫向發展黃金經濟圈 </span></span><br />\n-優先與本地黃色商家採購及合作<br />\n-一齊努力壯大黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n3 盈利會優先聘用於受社運影響人士<br />\n<br />\n4 與原創設計者推出聯乘產品 <br />\n-投資於香港人身上，發展本地品牌，推動本土創作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">5 以最信任的態度直接幫助受影響人士 <br />\n-採取小額資助計劃，以最快及最信任的方式給予需要支援的手足</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a6dd35c89b4f48feaf5fd894dc0201097d8da96","tid":1782964,"uid":8100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602dd8e3702f3a952cdc4260186a3c5df7995cd7","tid":1782964,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2807ae9150f5341f672d